Title: The White Warrior
Writer: Craig Johnson (book), Hunt Baldwin (developer), John Coveny (developer), Hunt Baldwin, John Coveny
Actors: Robert Taylor, Katee Sackhoff, Lou Diamond Phillips, Bailey Chase
Plot: Longmire investigates Branch's shooting, but Branch insists that he was shot by a dead man. Meanwhile, Henry goes to prison after being arrested for killing Longmire's wife's killer.
